<h1 id="-destroy-criteria-callback-">.destroy( <code>criteria</code> , [<code>callback</code>] )</h1>
<h3 id="purpose" permalink="purpose">Purpose</h3>
<p>Destroys all records in your database that match the given criteria.</p>
<h3 id="overview" permalink="overview">Overview</h3>
